g.text: an extension point for specializations of the individual tag name.
an extension point for specializations of the data tag
Data terms may have mixed content from any namespace.
Individuals and literals (data) are simple, constant terms, and may be used in slot keys.
an extension point for specializations of the expression tag name.
A collection of (ordered) arguments (optionally enclosed by <arg>) and/or
an extension point for specializations of the generalized list tag name.
Data terms are literals, and may have simple or complex datatypes.
The key (first position) in a slot
contains an interpreted term or data,
which may be simple or compound.
